---
source: crates/daemon/tests/cli_help.rs
expression: stdout
---
Route queued messages to a target label, optionally marking read and archiving

Usage: mxr route [OPTIONS] --to <TO_LABEL> --from-queue <FROM_QUEUE_LABEL> [MESSAGE_ID]...

Arguments:
  [MESSAGE_ID]...

Options:
      --search <SEARCH>
      --account <ACCOUNT>
      --to <TO_LABEL>
      --from-queue <FROM_QUEUE_LABEL>
      --archive
      --yes
      --dry-run
      --format <FORMAT>                [possible values: table, json, jsonl, csv, ids]
  -h, --help                           Print help
